OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy with showers or rain dying out
OL,7,Fthrough this evening. Then the rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,9,Fperiods. Cold with a slight frost in
OL,10,Fplaces.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mainly dry, bright morning
OL,13,Fwith some sunshine. Cloud will tend to
OL,14,Fbubble up through the day to give a
OL,15,Ffew afternoon showers between sunnier
OL,16,Fintervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
