OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,6,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy at first. Risk of
OL,8,Frain later on Thursday. Feeling warmer
OL,9,Fthan of late.
